Items.mt: <[>The sisters may look identical but are total opposites; Xiao Ying is naive and unaware of dangers of the world, like a fairy who fell to earth. The older sister is beautiful, mysterious and has overpowering love and hatred, like a little demon girl who seduces people! <]>
